Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 9, 2025, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 1052, H.D. 1, RELATING TO THE UNIVERSAL SERVICE PROGRAM.
S.D. 2, C.D. 1 ACT 202
