15 special fund to be known as the universal service fund to be
16 administered by the commission to implement the policies and
17 goals of universal service[—] through the universal service
18 program. The fund shall consist of contributions from the
19 sources identified in subsections (e) and (f). Interest earned
20 from the balance of the fund shall become a part of the fund.
